* 安德森曾參加過[[美國籃球協會|美國籃球協會]]的U16和U17訓練營，並於2010年被提名為{{link-en|美國國家發展籃球隊|USA Basketball|美國國家發展籃球隊}}的成員。<ref name=halley_03062012>{{cite news |last=Halley |first=Jim |title=USA Basketball names 10 players to Nike Hoop Summit team |date=March 6, 2012 |newspaper=USA Today |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/preps/basketball/story/2012-03-06/Nike-Hoop-Summit-names-US-roster/53388858/1 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6OB2DDKkJ?url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/preps/basketball/story/2012-03-06/Nike-Hoop-Summit-names-US-roster/53388858/1 |archivedate=2014-03-18 |deadurl=no |df= |accessdate=2018-01-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usabasketball.com/bios/anderson_kyle.html |title=USA Basketball: Kyle Anderson |date= |publisher=USA Basketball |author= |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6OB2GL0h7?url=http://www.usab.com/bios/anderson_kyle.html |archivedate=2014-03-18 |deadurl=yes |df= |accessdate=2018-01-06 }}</ref>在2012年，安德森代表{{link-en|美國國家籃球青年隊|USA Basketball|美國國家籃球青年隊}}參加當年的{{link-en|耐克籃球峰會|Nike Hoop Summit|耐吉籃球峰會}}。

* 凯尔·安德森有八分之一的[[中国人|中国人]]血统。他的外祖母[[玛丽安·福尔曼|玛丽安·福尔曼]]拥有一半的中国血统，玛丽安的父亲[[萨缪尔·李|萨缪尔·李]]，也就是安德森的外曾祖父，是一名中国客家人。萨缪尔·李在[[二战|二战]]期間為了躲避戰火，由[[中華民國_(大陸時期)|中国]]前往了[[牙买加|牙买加]]謀生，并与凯尔·安德森的曾外祖母[[艾吉塔·李|艾吉塔·李]]在當地结婚，之後便一直留在牙买加生活，生下了安德森的外祖母玛丽安。<ref>{{cite news |last=Zagoria |first=Adam |title=Like Jeremy Lin, UCLA-Bound Anderson Has Asian Heritage |date=February 18, 2012 |work=zagsblog.com |url=http://zagsblog.com/articles/like-jeremy-lin-ucla-bound-anderson-has-asian-heritage/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6OB6mzU5c?url=http://zagsblog.com/articles/like-jeremy-lin-ucla-bound-anderson-has-asian-heritage/ |archivedate=2014-03-19 |deadurl=no |df= |accessdate=2018-01-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Wharton |first=David |title=Not only do Bruins visit attractions in China, they become one |date=August 23, 2012 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2012/aug/23/sports/la-sp-0824-ucla-basketball-china-20120824 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6OB6ubEHO?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2012/aug/23/sports/la-sp-0824-ucla-basketball-china-20120824 |archivedate=2014-03-19 |deadurl=no |df= |accessdate=2018-01-06 }}</ref><ref>[https://tw.sports.appledaily.com/daily/20180803/38087398/ 客家血液呼喚 灰熊前鋒 尋根大作戰] {{Wayback|url=https://tw.sports.appledaily.com/daily/20180803/38087398/ |date=20181128142249 }}，蘋果日報，2018年8月3日</ref>

